Class PreferenceQueueService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.queue.pref.PreferenceQueueService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Lifecycle, LifecycleQueueService, QueueService

    public class PreferenceQueueService
extends Object
implements LifecycleQueueService
    An implementation of the queue service delegating on the synchronous and asynchronous implementations according to the processing preference.
